            <h3>
              <div class="note-toggle rr">
                <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/16074792/" class="note-unfolder">展开</a>
                <a href="javascript:void(0);" class="note-folder">收起</a>
              </div>
              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/16074792/" class="">第30页</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/50439734/" class=" " title="学而">学而</a>
                (在历史中走向哲学与诗……)
              
            </p>
            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="16074792">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">一切真诚都同时是伪装。而真诚与伪装的同一性，就是表演。</span>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2012-01-03 13:04</span>
                  
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="all hidden" style="display:none" >
                <blockquote><q>一切真诚都同时是伪装。而真诚与伪装的同一性，就是表演。</q></blockquote>
                  <div class="col-rec-con clearfix">
                    







